snippet: Fredrik Jacobson birdied the two toughest holes at Riviera on his way to a six-under-par 65 and a share of the lead with Sang-Moon Bae.
abstract: Fredrik Jacobson and Sang-Moon Bae share second-round lead at Northern Trust Open golf tournament in Los Angeles.
